Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:41.61,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませてまで　笑えなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:52.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう言って彼女はうつむいてたんだ　夜に泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:59.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷たく貼り付いて　凍えている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:06.91,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降り続く現実に　傘などない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.49,0:02:13.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生きてゆくことが　戦いなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:17.38,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな理由だけで　閉じ込められた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:20.27,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Heart　My Story
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.43,0:02:27.76,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泪のムコウが見えるの　輝いている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:34.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小さな窓には　あの頃みたいに　青い空が映る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:41.21,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah  ah　鳥のように　飛べはしないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:52.69,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませたとき　感じる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:54.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:03:00.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そっと目を閉じて　泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:41.61,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在伤害别人之前　不必强颜欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:52.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说着她低下头　在黑夜里哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:59.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷粘合在一起　浑身僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:06.91,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨下个不停　却没有伞来遮挡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.49,0:02:13.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己囚禁在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:17.38,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有战斗才能求生的因果之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:20.27,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心　我的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.43,0:02:27.76,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泪水的彼岸所见到的　是五彩光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:34.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的窗口　映照出那时蔚蓝的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:41.21,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　虽说不能像鸟儿一样自由翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:52.69,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害别人之后的那份心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:54.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不忘却
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:03:00.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻轻地闭上眼　哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:58.29,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}なくす事が拾うためなら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:04.09,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}別れるのは出逢うため
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:09.55,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}「さようなら」のあとには　きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:15.54,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}「こんにちは」と出逢うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:26.22,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}緑色芝生に寝ころんでいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:37.45,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}動物も一緒にゴロゴロしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:45.74,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}今日は良い事がたくさんあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:58.29,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}若丢弃是为了捡回
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:04.09,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}那分别就是为了相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:09.55,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}告别之后　一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:15.54,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}迎来重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:26.22,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}想躺在那绿色的草坪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:37.45,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}和动物们一起悠闲自得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:45.74,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}今天喜事多…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是电磁场光共振部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.56,0:00:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.84,0:00:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如其名  进行狙击！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已确认卫星兵器被破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.32,0:01:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密已脱离战斗区域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.13,0:01:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是多亏了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.49,0:01:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是Celestial Being的战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.69,0:01:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E探测器有反应  是敌机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.69,0:01:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们得为击落Memento Mori赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.04,0:01:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:12.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}#14  听到歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.99,0:03:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已查明同步卫星轨道上发生的爆炸事故
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起因是反联邦势力的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了对应日益猖獗的恐怖袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦议会将直接管理联邦军和独立治安维持部队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.32,0:03:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在全世界规模进行防卫网的强化…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Memento Mori被击落了么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.41,0:03:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙的卡塔隆大部分都被消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了实现统一世界的永久和平
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.37,0:03:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都必须消灭Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果继续容忍他们的存在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反政府势力就有重新取得优势的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.99,0:03:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汇合地点  应该是在这附近的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.29,0:04:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这机体是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色的GN粒子！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:33.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi  好久不见了  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·崔尼蒂！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成个好男人了啊  妮娜很动心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…  等一下啊  刚才不是才帮了你么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  你们的船貌似落到地球上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把战斗资料传送给你  看了的话连行踪也… 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…怎么这么急啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是这么性急  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了  被甩了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是吹的什么风啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.94,0:05:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然特地到中东来见我 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有想要传达给在军队里担任监查任务的你的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情报？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队中有人在策划发动政变
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我认为对联邦政府的政策持反感态度的人很多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到竟然会搞政变…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦政府已经成了A-LAWS的傀儡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要让世人们清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢尔盖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O…O-Raizer呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力？  什么时候到地上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥呀！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对监视用光学迷彩已恢复  展开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  让OO-Raizer启动  击退了拉格朗治3的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从A-LAWS那知道了联邦使用卫星兵器的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并前往执行破坏任务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然顺利干掉了  但是却受到敌人的奇袭而落到大气圈内
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:06:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地上迫降
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还与刹那驾驶的OO-Raizer走散了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这么回事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是惨到家了么！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:10.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说嘛  大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星兵器已经被破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是在用尽GN粒子的时候受到的奇袭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外敌人的部队还投入了新型MA
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:25.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有利用船中弹的冲击加速
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.16,0:07:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并利用烟雾伪装  将船体降落到地上…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些皇·李·诺瑞加带来的转机的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们早就被干掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条命没丢就该谢天谢地了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那托勒密的情况呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然引擎没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但航行系统  武器控制  通信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探测器之类的损伤严重…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:54.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…  如果这种时候被敌人袭击的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.17,0:07:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  我把吃的拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:07:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这也太散漫了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  阿里路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让玛丽小姐参加战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情已经过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且玛丽也接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.37,0:08:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…  请不要让这种事再发生第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星兵器虽然被破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这边损伤也不小
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最糟的情况恐怕是要借用支部的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在跟谁打电话么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一些俗事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.87,0:08:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么A-LAWS能那么准确的掌握普特利麦奥斯的位置…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:09:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  利塔娜小姐是在怀疑我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  只是有这个疑问而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.72,0:09:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  还有  叫我亚琉就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…  那么叫我莱尔就行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:14.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔·迪兰地  是我的本名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密的反应…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这就是卫星兵器的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也都是改革者计划之下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…  那家伙为什么会在这里！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼…  跟过来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军的一部分在策划着政变！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的吗？池田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情报来源是我做记者时的老朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.13,0:10:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个值得信赖的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于无法忍受A-LAWS的恶行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政变派想要跟我们进行接触
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然会谈场所似乎是指定在中东的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  克劳斯  也可能是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意相信想要纠正联邦的恶政的他们的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且想要回应他们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这首歌是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好像是玛丽娜公主把孩子们的话搜集起来写的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种状况还能唱歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:51.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切…  到底想到哪儿去？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个方向是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁吉斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底准备做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里·阿尔·沙谢斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁吉斯的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  已经是克鲁吉斯的小哥了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里·阿尔·沙谢斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然跑到改革者那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  佣兵只要有人雇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:53.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是看报酬挑工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的战斗是没有意义的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊  不过你应该理解不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天是带了个想见你的人来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我的雇主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改革者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫李本兹  李本兹·阿尔马克
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久违了  刹那·F·清荣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索兰·伊布拉希姆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  对你来说跟我是初次见面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过对我来说可不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在十一年前就见过你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  就在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的人类之间相互争斗而不得自拔的战场上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个拼命躲避着的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在注视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从MS的驾驶舱里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难  难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台机体…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在O-Gundam里的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次武力介入是O-Gundam的性能测试
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然为了保密  在场的所有人原本都应该处理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我却救了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.09,0:14:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为注视着O-Gundam…注视着我的你那双眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我留下很深的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此  通过吠陀推荐你成为Gundam Meister的也是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让我道谢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的使命已经完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:09.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是时候该还给我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那原本就是该由我搭乘的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.69,0:15:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我拒绝！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板  我的生存价值就是战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙  有两台未确认的MS从不同方向过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特  让阿里路亚和特瑞亚出击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了…了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  我们的位置被…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:16:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee  特瑞亚·埃德  出发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios  阿里路亚·哈普提兹姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始迎击行动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀的状况…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:26.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fang！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有破绽！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭那种身体状况还能有这种动作…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊  那家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:17:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮击型  不会让你射击的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有哈里路亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大气层内还得计算对方的机动性啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你有吠陀的辅助！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亚·埃德  你可是改革者！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来跟我们一起贯彻使命！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.09,0:17:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:53.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…改革者的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争在蔓延…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了  公主殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想  要是你们的歌能传达给大家就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就得唱出来啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.50,0:18:18.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我只能做到这些…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也要做到这些…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:25.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同类相残虽不忍目睹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也有不得不为之的使命！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.86,0:18:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能相让的东西我们也有！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关闭了Field？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM吗  就凭这种程度！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟Nadleeh那时候不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是以自己的意志  展现出这个姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这机体…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seraphim Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:10.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Seraphim:和Seravee一样，是炽天使的另一种说法）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想对同类刀刃相向吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对！我是人类！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布林格！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.89,0:19:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布林格·斯塔比提！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  特瑞亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  得寸进尺…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯  是MS！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:19:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来为我们护航吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.64,0:20:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.94,0:20:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就算是人质了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下你就无法出手…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.93,0:20:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fang！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.99,0:20:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了…歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌声…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:57.71,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}なくす事が拾うためなら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:03.30,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}別れるのは出逢うため
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:08.80,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}「さようなら」のあとには　きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.05,0:21:14.74,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}「こんにちは」と出逢うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:25.77,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}緑色芝生に寝ころんでいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:36.74,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}動物も一緒にゴロゴロしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:48.00,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}今日は良い事がたくさんあったから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:59.20,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}明日も良い事がたくさんあるように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.43,0:22:04.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}お日様出て　夕日きれいで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.95,0:22:10.25,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}星に願い明日が来る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:15.57,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}どうして行っちゃうの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.05,0:22:21.85,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}一緒に帰ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:57.71,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}若丢弃是为了捡回
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:03.30,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}那分别就是为了相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:08.80,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}告别之后　一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.05,0:21:14.74,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}迎来重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:25.77,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8\fs18}想躺在那绿色的草坪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:36.74,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}和动物们一起悠闲自得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:48.00,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}今天喜事多多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:59.20,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}愿明天也一样欢喜连连
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.43,0:22:04.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}太阳升起了　在美丽的晚霞照耀下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.95,0:22:10.25,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}向星星许愿明天快快来临
